{
  "stem": "24346.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And sure enough, our papers were processed, and they called us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was another camp, Butzbach, where they took you into that camp-- means you're waiting only for the ship to arrive.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when the ships arrive, they take you to the port city, and you travel.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at that time, we were with the little girl-- four, she was born in July-- that was, yeah, February-- well, six, seven months, eight months, and they called us to come to the United States.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we went through all the tests, all the questions, all the answers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they obviously worked with our relatives.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Our papers were not strictly from the American government.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was in conjunction with the uncles, because our uncle had to guarantee-- at that time, they had to guarantee, before they let you in, that you will not fall, and the United States government will not have to support you-- welfare, whatever.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my uncle had to guarantee that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he had a friend who was an insurance man, who was also a notary.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He notarized the papers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They went into a butcher.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said my nephew is coming, he needs a job.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they told him, he wouldn't bother you, because he knows what to do and he'll find-- sign us, so we can come.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So this butcher, I remember, in Washington Heights signed for me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my uncle's friend, an insurance man and also a public notary, signed the papers, legit.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They sent me that the job is ready.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So in conjunction with them, between the two-- the United States government and my uncle-- the papers were fixed, and they took us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we went and left for the United States in March of 1945, ah, '49.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
